{
  "_comment": "Per-site sync config. version source feeds SITE.version in src/lib/site.ts. source types: gh-release (latest GitHub release tag, the v prefix is inferred from the site's current value), skill-count (count skill dirs in the repo), manual (never auto-touched).",
